WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.394
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.394 --> 00:00:04.759
I have another video for you all today.

00:00:05.096 --> 00:00:12.711
I've been praying early this morning and seeking Him about what to do for a video for you all.

00:00:13.088 --> 00:00:20.039
When I was praying, the Lord showed me more about what's coming.

00:00:20.296 --> 00:00:53.262
I was going to deliver a lot of this word to you and tell you about more preparation, but when I was at the sink doing the dishes again tonight, the Lord spoke to me and He said, 'Brandon, they need a foundation.

00:00:53.262 --> 00:01:02.131
They're going to have to have a foundation of the Word.

00:01:05.251 --> 00:01:21.920
You can keep delivering the word and telling them what's coming, son, but I'm warning you to pray over this stuff.

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:49.799
' This is what I'm trying to tell you: the gross darkness that's coming and the things that would be like throwing gas on the fire for you all.

00:01:49.799 --> 00:02:28.360
I know people are curious about what's coming, and it's important to know, but it's more important for you to have a foundation of the Word and know how to stand on it for what's coming than anything else.

00:02:29.365 --> 00:03:14.613
You can know what's coming and be totally destroyed, or you can have a foundation of the Word of God and be able to resist, stand fast, and know how to believe for things to have victory in this storm.

00:03:27.849 --> 00:03:56.599
If you don't have the Word and a concrete foundation—not a sandy soil or quicksand foundation—we're going to have a Word-based foundation of solid rock so that you can build your house on it and the storms of life will not blow down your home.

00:04:03.947 --> 00:04:23.774
But if you do not have a foundation in the Word and it's on sand, your house is going to be swept away when the wave comes.

00:04:23.774 --> 00:04:34.375
We'll get to all that stuff later; it's not important right now.

00:04:34.375 --> 00:04:46.747
What's important is for you to understand: have you sat at the feet of Jesus today?

00:04:49.671 --> 00:05:02.920
Have you sat with Him and started to develop a relationship with the Father sitting at His feet?

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:17.239
It is so important that you take the time every day to get in the Word and read your Bible.

00:05:17.239 --> 00:05:23.328
Find scriptures that pertain to what you're believing for.

00:05:23.328 --> 00:05:31.400
Like I've said over and over, start reading the New Testament all the way through.

00:05:45.726 --> 00:05:46.223
Read two and three chapters a day.

00:05:46.223 --> 00:05:53.063
Spend 20 to 30 minutes inside the Word.

00:05:53.063 --> 00:06:02.514
If you can spend 30 minutes on Facebook, Instagram, and YouTube watching these videos, you can take 20 minutes for the Word.

00:06:10.030 --> 00:06:23.690
I would rather you not watch any videos at all—mine or anyone else's on the prophetic network on YouTube—and take that time for the Word instead.

00:06:23.690 --> 00:06:42.377
If you say you don't have enough time, then don't watch my video; get in the Word.

00:06:56.680 --> 00:06:57.080
It's more important for you to get in the Word than to watch me or anybody else.

00:07:00.074 --> 00:07:04.739
The Word is the priority in your life, period.

00:07:04.739 --> 00:07:05.672
Pray.

00:07:09.372 --> 00:07:12.704
It has to be the priority for what's coming, or you will not make it.

00:07:12.704 --> 00:07:26.923
I'm just telling you, that may sound scary, but it needs to scare you because gross darkness is coming.

00:07:26.923 --> 00:07:42.148
Very dark times are coming for the world, though not for the body of Christ.

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:56.860
Just like it says in Isaiah: 'Arise, shine, for thy light is come, and the glory of the Lord is risen upon thee.

00:07:56.860 --> 00:08:17.240
' The rest of the verse talks about great darkness on the earth because of sin and gross darkness on the people.

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:38.128
If there's really bad darkness on these people and you're the light, how are you going to stay in the light?

00:08:40.806 --> 00:08:46.977
Have you sat at the feet of Jesus today?

00:09:00.579 --> 00:09:04.164
Have you listened to Him and talked to Him about your life, your direction, and where you're supposed to be living?

00:09:04.164 --> 00:09:18.707
Are you living in a high-rise in New York City while God is trying to tell you to live in the country?

00:09:18.707 --> 00:09:29.473
Are you in downtown Chicago and God is saying you need to move?

00:09:33.816 --> 00:09:52.262
You might have a good job, but you're not seeking Him on another job while He's trying to tell you to move.

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:05.720
I'm telling you, you need to be in the place that God has for you.

00:10:05.720 --> 00:10:24.205
Maybe He wants you in those cities because you're going to be a light there, but maybe He's trying to tell you to do something else.

00:10:26.035 --> 00:10:29.817
You just need to hear Him.

00:10:29.817 --> 00:10:42.892
People say they don't hear His voice at all; it's because you're not in the Word.

00:10:42.892 --> 00:11:10.226
I was listening to statistics from Pastor Steve, who said 97% of all Christians don't read their Bible on a daily basis and only 3% have read the Word all the way through.

00:11:10.226 --> 00:11:19.904
When I heard that statistic at church, I thought, 'This is serious.

00:11:19.904 --> 00:11:35.509
' The foundation of the Word is what's going to get you through hard times.

00:11:35.509 --> 00:11:40.777
You have got to get that Bible out and read it.

00:11:40.777 --> 00:11:52.693
If you say it's too hard to understand, get a translation that you do understand.

00:11:59.465 --> 00:12:02.480
It may be the New Living Translation—there are all kinds of really good translations.

00:12:02.480 --> 00:12:07.268
Let's not get religious about this.

00:12:07.268 --> 00:12:19.953
If you don't understand the King James Version, find a Bible that ministers to you.

00:12:19.953 --> 00:12:34.535
If you're a teenager and you can only understand something like The Message Bible, that's better than nothing.

00:12:46.429 --> 00:12:48.900
Read the Word.

00:13:03.199 --> 00:13:03.399
It may be modernized, but it's the Word of God and it's going to change your life.

00:13:04.399 --> 00:13:10.840
The Amplified Bible is also a good version that will help you.

00:13:10.840 --> 00:13:23.990
I read all kinds of different translations because everything ministers to me differently.

00:13:23.990 --> 00:13:33.945
Let's just get in the Word and not be petty.

00:13:33.945 --> 00:13:41.720
Read two or three chapters every day.

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:46.960
When I talk about practicing the presence of the Lord, I'm talking about visualizing Him being there with you.

00:13:46.960 --> 00:13:54.356
Talk to Him like you'd talk to your son or daughter.

00:13:54.356 --> 00:13:56.230
Visualize that Jesus Christ is living on the inside of you.

00:13:56.230 --> 00:14:08.219
I'm not saying to pretend; Jesus is real and He is living on the inside of you.

00:14:12.680 --> 00:14:19.720
You practice His presence by thinking, 'Jesus, how is Your day today?

00:14:19.720 --> 00:14:27.874
' Visualize Him sitting there with you.

00:14:27.874 --> 00:14:45.928
Think about it in your head: Jesus is in me, He is with me, and I'm going to practice talking to Him.

00:14:45.928 --> 00:14:51.187
Don't act like He's far away.

00:14:51.187 --> 00:15:08.030
He said, 'I'll never leave you nor forsake you; lo, I am with you always, even unto the end of the world.

00:15:08.030 --> 00:15:12.971
' That means He is dwelling in you.

00:15:18.491 --> 00:15:27.920
The very atmosphere can get charged with the power of the Holy Ghost if you start worshiping and meditating on His Word.

00:15:33.405 --> 00:15:35.959
Lord, I want to know You more; teach me Your ways.

00:15:37.582 --> 00:15:50.576
The Bible says His sheep will know His voice, and a stranger's voice they will not follow.

00:15:50.576 --> 00:15:55.351
How do you know someone's voice?

00:15:55.895 --> 00:15:58.019
You become familiar with them.

00:15:58.019 --> 00:16:03.745
If my wife calls me, I know her voice immediately.

00:16:03.745 --> 00:16:11.268
If my son calls, I know immediately it's him.

00:16:11.268 --> 00:16:12.553
Why?

00:16:12.553 --> 00:16:22.514
Because you've spent time with them and developed a relationship over years.

00:16:22.514 --> 00:16:33.239
It's the same way you develop a relationship with the Lord; you spend time with Him.

00:16:38.232 --> 00:16:48.779
The more time you spend in prayer and reading His Word, the more you're going to know His voice.

00:16:48.779 --> 00:16:57.240
For instance, my grandfather was one of my best friends.

00:17:05.339 --> 00:17:05.679
I knew his voice perfectly, but he passed away 12 years ago.

00:17:06.675 --> 00:17:16.319
I began to forget how his voice sounded until I found an old video recording of him.

00:17:16.319 --> 00:17:29.600
I heard his voice and started crying because it was so precious to me.

00:17:29.600 --> 00:17:37.994
Once you go back to it, you don't forget it again.

00:17:37.994 --> 00:17:48.662
But if you don't spend quality time with that voice, you start to forget the pitch.

00:17:48.662 --> 00:17:55.036
You've got to read the Bible and pray.

00:17:55.036 --> 00:18:05.635
Let's make a plan to get in the Word every day.

00:18:05.635 --> 00:18:19.140
We can start it now for the Jewish New Year; let's do it in Rosh Hashanah.

00:18:19.140 --> 00:18:25.270
We don't have to wait for January.

00:18:25.270 --> 00:18:43.573
If you feed your flesh three times a day, but your spirit is starving, you're in trouble.

00:18:43.573 --> 00:18:53.911
Most people only feed their spirit for 30 minutes on Sunday.

00:18:53.911 --> 00:19:13.784
If you go to a mega church and the only Bible time you have is reading scriptures on the teleprompter, that's not enough.

00:19:13.784 --> 00:19:22.247
Your spirit needs to eat in the morning and at night.

00:19:22.247 --> 00:19:34.410
If you start feeding your spirit, your life is going to change because God is the Word.

00:19:34.410 --> 00:19:42.840
He inspired those words; they are Him, and they bring life into you.

00:19:42.840 --> 00:19:50.311
It's like taking a spiritual bath every time you get in that Bible.

00:19:50.311 --> 00:19:54.106
Renew your mind in it.

00:19:54.106 --> 00:19:59.920
Pray and take a big spiritual drink.

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:08.052
If you do this, it will change your life.

00:20:08.052 --> 00:20:19.093
If you don't hear the voice of God, it's because you're not spending time with Him.

00:20:19.351 --> 00:20:23.211
He is no respecter of persons.

00:20:23.211 --> 00:20:26.106
If He talks to me, He will talk to you.

00:20:26.106 --> 00:20:38.733
My 8-year-old daughter hears the voice of the Lord because I'm teaching her at a young age.

00:20:38.733 --> 00:20:53.617
He didn't make it hard; you just get in the Word, pray, and meditate on it.

00:20:53.617 --> 00:21:03.440
This is not something you do once; it's something you do every day.

00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:18.782
There are 365 days a year, 24 hours in a day, 52 weeks in a year.

00:21:18.782 --> 00:21:25.929
This is your staple, just like eating and breathing.

00:21:25.929 --> 00:21:30.808
Read your Bible every day, period.

00:21:30.808 --> 00:21:47.868
By this time next year, right before the presidential elections in America, you will look back and remember what I told you.

00:21:56.880 --> 00:21:57.280
You will say, 'My life has forever changed.

00:21:57.280 --> 00:22:04.186
' I challenge you to a year of this.

00:22:06.070 --> 00:22:15.320
You don't go to the gym just once to lose weight; you have to go to the spiritual gym.

00:22:15.320 --> 00:22:22.160
Eat the Word and meditate on it.

00:22:22.160 --> 00:22:25.381
Lift those spiritual weights.

00:22:25.381 --> 00:22:33.200
In a year—or even 30 days—see where you are spiritually.

00:22:42.191 --> 00:22:42.480
I give you a 30-day challenge starting right now.

00:22:42.480 --> 00:22:47.336
Where will you be on October 6th?

00:22:47.336 --> 00:22:57.057
Start now, reading three or four chapters and meditating on a verse that stands out to you.

00:22:57.057 --> 00:22:58.995
Memorize it.

00:22:58.995 --> 00:23:11.568
'The grass withers and the flower fades, but the word of the Lord remains forever.

00:23:11.568 --> 00:23:18.209
' Get that inside your soul.

00:23:18.209 --> 00:23:33.894
Memorize First Peter, memorize Isaiah, and know that 'Greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world.

00:23:33.894 --> 00:23:54.640
' Know Second Timothy 1:7: 'God has not given you a spirit of fear, but of power, and of love, and of a sound mind.

00:23:54.640 --> 00:24:03.015
' You need those scriptures for what's coming.

00:24:03.015 --> 00:24:14.160
When the devourer comes knocking at your door, it's too late to start reading.

00:24:14.160 --> 00:24:20.320
You can't say, 'Hold on, Mr.

00:24:20.320 --> 00:24:29.306
Devil, I've got to get in my Bible for a bit.

00:24:29.306 --> 00:24:33.190
' He’s already there.

00:24:47.950 --> 00:24:48.305
You have to submit yourself unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

00:24:49.725 --> 00:25:00.493
You need to know that He's made you more than a conqueror through Christ Jesus.

00:25:00.493 --> 00:25:10.384
Your mountain has to hear your voice—the power of God in your voice.

00:25:10.384 --> 00:25:21.740
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:25:21.740 --> 00:25:48.765
It doesn't do any good to know what's coming if you don't have a foundation in the Word, because the winds and waves of life are coming.

00:26:00.010 --> 00:26:00.320
You better have a revelation of who He is so you can understand your covenant.

00:26:00.320 --> 00:26:32.770
It's time to get a foundation so that you can stand on the Word and know that you have not seen the righteous forsaken nor his seed begging bread.

00:26:32.770 --> 00:26:40.720
If He takes care of the sparrow, He will take care of you.

00:26:40.720 --> 00:26:59.095
If He multiplied for the five thousand, and if He provided for the widow with Elijah, He'll provide for you.

00:26:59.095 --> 00:27:17.120
We've got to get in the Word so you can hear Him.

00:27:17.120 --> 00:27:53.480
Father, I just thank You right now in the name of Jesus for my brothers and sisters.

00:28:03.712 --> 00:28:51.307
I lift them up before You and thank You for the blood of Jesus Christ that covers them from head to toe.

00:28:51.307 --> 00:29:38.804
We take authority over the spirit of fear, torment, depression, and anxiety.

00:29:38.804 --> 00:30:16.560
We cast our cares upon You, for we know You care for us.

00:30:16.560 --> 00:31:11.203
You loved us enough to send Your Son to die for us, so You will provide for us.

00:31:11.203 --> 00:32:05.608
Father, help these people have a hunger for a revelation of Your Word.

00:32:05.608 --> 00:32:32.260
I plead the blood over their ears that they have spiritual ears to hear what the Spirit is saying.

00:32:32.260 --> 00:32:47.793
Holy Spirit, I thank You that You're stirring in them and getting them excited about Your Word.

00:32:54.712 --> 00:33:05.045
I pray that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened, according to Ephesians, and flooded with light today.

00:33:11.568 --> 00:33:14.520
I plead the blood over their minds, their wills, and their emotions.

00:33:14.520 --> 00:33:20.810
Give them wisdom like Solomon.

00:33:20.810 --> 00:33:26.408
No torment comes nigh them.

00:33:36.535 --> 00:33:39.440
Father, I thank You that as they seek You, they will find You.

00:33:50.140 --> 00:33:53.489
I thank You that Your presence is filling their house right now.

00:33:53.489 --> 00:34:07.399
Show them how much You love them and give them the peace that passes understanding.

00:34:11.130 --> 00:34:17.504
I thank You that You meet their needs—spiritually, physically, financially, and emotionally.

00:34:24.249 --> 00:34:24.544
I come in agreement for their finances and for healing.

00:34:24.544 --> 00:34:29.470
By Your stripes, we are healed.

00:34:30.429 --> 00:34:38.090
You were wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities.

00:34:38.090 --> 00:34:49.324
We sit at Your feet today and ask, 'Lord, what's on Your heart today?

00:34:49.324 --> 00:34:53.391
' We put You first.

00:34:53.391 --> 00:35:01.786
We breathe in those pages; we breathe You in, Father.

00:35:01.786 --> 00:35:05.640
We drink from the well.

00:35:05.640 --> 00:35:14.600
Lord, we're thirsty for a mighty move of God.

00:35:14.600 --> 00:35:29.855
Pour out Your Holy Ghost; I want to see the hand of God move mightily.

00:35:29.855 --> 00:35:37.084
I'm hungry for a move of God.

00:35:37.084 --> 00:35:45.663
Fill my cup, Lord; I lift it up.

00:35:45.663 --> 00:35:54.230
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

00:35:54.230 --> 00:36:02.946
Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more.

00:36:02.946 --> 00:36:12.750
Fill my cup, fill it up, and make me whole.

00:36:33.200 --> 00:36:33.720
He inhabits the praises of His people.

00:36:43.210 --> 00:36:47.169
If you enter His courts with praise, the manifestation of His glory comes.

00:36:47.169 --> 00:36:54.640
When praises go up, blessings come down.

00:37:02.920 --> 00:37:03.133
Worship Him first with thanksgiving.

00:37:04.020 --> 00:37:06.867
Thank Him for what you have.

00:37:06.867 --> 00:37:22.200
Don't go in like a spoiled brat acting like He owes you; He's already done it all.

00:37:22.200 --> 00:37:35.267
Even if I'm just dust, I refuse to let a rock do my job.

00:37:35.267 --> 00:37:51.613
Let everything that has breath praise the Lord, for He is worthy regardless of your circumstances.

00:37:51.613 --> 00:37:58.529
Get in that place of worship right now.

00:37:58.529 --> 00:38:13.505
Even if you only have a cracker to eat, be thankful and watch Him move on your behalf.

00:38:13.505 --> 00:38:23.680
I remember when my parents had no money and no food.

00:38:31.160 --> 00:38:34.629
We were hungry, staying in a hotel with cockroaches, and Dad had no job.

00:38:34.629 --> 00:38:51.074
Mom pulled all the coins out of her purse just to get some cheap tacos.

00:38:53.965 --> 00:39:07.129
My sister went back to that coin purse, praying, and found a supernatural $20 bill in there.

00:39:14.825 --> 00:39:18.927
We rejoiced because we got to eat!

00:39:23.011 --> 00:39:24.366
God comes through.

00:39:27.610 --> 00:39:32.434
He's been faithful to me when I've had nothing.

00:39:38.657 --> 00:39:39.994
Don't give up.

00:39:41.720 --> 00:39:44.489
You've got to learn how to believe by faith.

00:39:50.257 --> 00:39:53.399
God's going to do an accelerated time for you because Jesus is coming.

00:39:59.208 --> 00:40:04.560
I bless you all in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:40:06.053 --> 00:40:12.709
I believe for healing and prosperity for you.

00:40:25.787 --> 00:40:30.507
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:40:30.507 --> 00:40:33.576
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:40:33.912 --> 00:40:36.240
We will see you next time.

00:40:36.240 --> 00:40:40.719
Have a blessed and wonderful day.

00:40:40.719 --> 00:40:42.079
Bye-bye.
